Package: riverweed
Title: Aquatic macrophyte growth models for Podostemum ceratophyllum
Version: 1.0.0
Published: 
Authors@R: 
        c(person(given = "Lee H.", family = "Dietterich", , "lee.dietterich@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000")),
        person(given = "S. Kyle", family = "McKay",
           role = c("aut"),
           email = "kyle.mckay@usace.army.mil",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2703-3841")))
Maintainer: Lee H. Dietterich <lee.dietterich@gmail.com>
Description: This package quantifies growth of aquatic macrophytes in rivers. 
    The package was designed around hornleaf riverweed (Podostemum ceratophyllum), 
    but modules may be useful for other taxa.
URL: GitHub (<https://github.com/USACE-WRISES>)
Vignettes: Original documentation can be found in Dietterich and McKay (2023).
